line_1: Let that ay be your border:
line_2: To haud the wretch in order;

line_1: When rakes begin on blasphemy to border,
line_2: Bromley and Hanmer cry aloud — to order.
The poet felt a strange disorder:

line_1: Of Saturn's ring bright shines the border;
line_2: Orion has his belt in order;

line_1: The Gard'ner industrious trims out his Border,
line_2: Puts each odoriferous Plant in it's Order;

line_1: With accents that on harshness border,
line_2: And words that love would call to order;
